Type of Feat: General
Prerequisite: None.
Specifics: This feat allows effective use of all martial weapons. The martial weapons list includes the battleaxe, greataxe, greatsword, handaxe, heavy flail, kukri, light flail, light hammer, longbow, longsword, rapier, scimitar, scythe, short sword, shortbow, throwing axe, warhammer, and warmace.
Normal: A character cannot equip weapons they are not proficient in.
Use: Barbarians, fighters, paladins, and rangers are automatically proficient with all martial weapons. 